  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "1FPttaWIGDZhOrxR3iaGEmCkxp0=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:29.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "## Collaboration manifest structure\n\nA new Swarm feed is created per collaboration target, owned by the initiator:\n\n```\nTopic:  ph:v2:collab:<driveId>         (drive-level)\n        ph:v2:collab:<driveId>:<docId> (doc-level)\nOwner:  the collaboration initiator\n```\n\nThe payload is written ACT-protected, with grantees set to all participants' Bee node public keys:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"kind\": \"drive\" | \"document\",\n  \"driveId\": \"\u2026\",\n  \"documentId\": \"\u2026\",\n  \"participants\": [\n    { \"address\": \"0xA\u2026\", \"beeNodePublicKey\": \"02\u2026\", \"joinedAt\": \"\u2026\" },\n    { \"address\": \"0xB\u2026\", \"beeNodePublicKey\": \"02\u2026\", \"joinedAt\": \"\u2026\" }\n  ],\n  \"createdAt\": \"\u2026\",\n  \"version\": 1\n}\n```\n\nA participant joining or leaving is expressed as a new manifest revision by the initiator. Today only the initiator can rewrite their manifest feed \u2014 future work may allow any participant to amend via a Merkle-log or signed-append convention.",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:29.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:29.000Z"
    }
  },
